Algorithm reference (PRD §6 Public Contracts):
```rust
pub fn provider_for_model(model: Option<&str>) -> Provider {
    let lower = model.unwrap_or("").to_lowercase();
    if lower.split('-').any(|t| t == "grok") {
        Provider::Grok
    } else {
        Provider::Claude
    }
}
```
